=head1 DESCRIPTION

A list of HTTP headers that CloudFront includes as values for the
C<Access-Control-Expose-Headers> HTTP response header.

For more information about the C<Access-Control-Expose-Headers> HTTP
response header, see Access-Control-Expose-Headers
(https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Expose-Headers)
in the MDN Web Docs.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Items => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The list of HTTP headers. You can specify C<*> to expose all headers.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Quantity => Int

The number of HTTP headers in the list.



